description: pre-aggregated data for a standard run execution metric that applies to a journey.

parameters.name: ApplicationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the application. This identifier is displayed as the Project ID on the Amazon Pinpoint console.

parameters.name: JourneyId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the journey.

parameters.name: RunId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the journey run.

nested_items.name: JourneyRunExecutionMetricsResponse
nested_items.description: Provides the results of a query that retrieved the data for a standard execution metric that applies to a journey run, and provides information about that query.

nested_items.name: ApplicationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the application that the metric applies to.

nested_items.name: JourneyId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the journey that the metric applies to.

nested_items.name: LastEvaluatedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time, in ISO 8601 format, when Amazon Pinpoint last evaluated the journey run and updated the data for the metric.

nested_items.name: RunId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the journey run that the metric applies to.
